00:12:03.055 --> 00:12:04.598
‪Petinju Hong Woo-jin
‪dengan celana merah

00:12:04.682 --> 00:12:06.684
‪melawan petinju Jung Jae-hoon
‪dengan celana biru.

00:12:06.767 --> 00:12:07.768
‪Masuk lebih dalam.

00:12:07.852 --> 00:12:09.562
‪Ah, pukulan body kedua sisi bagus.

00:12:09.645 --> 00:12:11.188
Betul. Hong Woo-jin bersandar pada tali.

00:12:11.272 --> 00:12:13.733
‪Ah, dia memukul body kedua sisi
‪dan, ah, memprovokasi.

00:12:13.816 --> 00:12:16.277
‪Ah, begitu. Dia masih menunjukkan ketenangan.

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.987
'Pukul kalau bisa.'
Ya.

00:12:18.070 --> 00:12:19.321
‪'Kau sudah cukup...'

00:12:19.405 --> 00:12:20.239
‪Ah, body shot!

00:12:20.322 --> 00:12:21.157
‪Benar!

00:12:21.240 --> 00:12:22.450
‪Serangan body yang bersih masuk.

00:12:22.533 --> 00:12:23.993
‪Nah, wajah, kena!

00:12:24.535 --> 00:12:26.537
Dia menjatuhkannya! Hong Woo-jin,
Benar!

00:12:26.620 --> 00:12:29.039
‪One-two straight dari double kanan.

00:12:29.123 --> 00:12:30.332
Gerakannya juga sangat...

00:12:30.416 --> 00:12:32.042
Pertunjukannya sangat luar biasa.

00:12:32.126 --> 00:12:33.753
Ah, KO.

00:12:33.836 --> 00:12:35.463
‪Ya, pertandingan selanjutnya adalah
‪antara Kim Gun-woo

00:12:35.546 --> 00:12:37.465
melawan Kim Rae-hyun.

00:12:37.548 --> 00:12:39.550
‪Super rookie Kim Gun-woo
‪dengan celana biru.

00:12:39.633 --> 00:12:42.511
‪Betul. Kim Gun-woo melakukan
‪cover sambil...

00:12:42.595 --> 00:12:43.512
‪Body shot!

00:12:43.596 --> 00:12:45.556
Body!
Dia berlutut!

00:12:46.557 --> 00:12:48.142
‪Betul. Tepat mengenai ulu hati...

00:12:48.225 --> 00:12:50.186
Ah, pertandingan selesai.
Betul.

00:12:50.269 --> 00:12:51.729
‪Dengan satu pukulan itu,
‪pertandingan berakhir.

00:12:51.812 --> 00:12:54.440
